  "instructions": [
    "In a copper mug combine fish stock, white wine, Dijon mustard, soy sauce, and brown sugar; stir until the sugar dissolves.",
    "Add ground Sichuan peppercorns, red pepper flakes, and a splash of infuse oil; let the mixture come to a gentle simmer.",
    "While the broth simmers, sauté diced onion and minced garlic in a separate pan until translucent, then transfer to the copper mug.",
    "Season the broth with salt and pepper, adjusting to taste.",
    "Gently place the cod fillets into the simmering broth, ensuring they are fully submerged.",
    "Cover the mug and cook for 6 minutes, or until the cod flakes easily with a fork.",
    "Remove the mug from heat, ladle the stew into individual glasses, and garnish with a light drizzle of infuse oil.",
    "Serve immediately, pairing with crusty bread or a simple side salad."
  ],
